    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in showroom-floor condition. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by factory mats since day one. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions perfectly, reflecting its meticulous maintenance history. The engine bay is detailed and clean, showing no signs of age or use. This car has never seen inclement weather and has been handled with extreme care by a single enthusiast owner. Included in the sale are all original service records, two keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom-fit breathable car cover. For the buyer seeking a specimen that is indistinguishable from new, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
