      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in absolute showroom condition. This unit has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards, featuring an unblemished exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system operates with the precision and refinement expected of a vehicle in this superior state. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
