    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW M-division engineering. Powered by the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, the powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to a stratospheric 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. This specimen is in showroom-grade condition, featuring a reinforced rear subframe, updated rod bearings, and a flawless factory finish. Mechanically unassailable and cosmetically pristine, it offers the definitive analog driving experience for the discerning collector.",
